{"tid":858222,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"數碼暴龍第一輯真係百看不厭","createTime":"2018-10-11T15:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T18:52:43.000Z","uid":117552,"like":58,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"805b34f04a1d3d9e7215916c255da7e6864e807b","tid":858222,"uid":117552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T15:44:36.000Z","msg":"八個細路都有故事<br />\n太一做領袖而大和就做對抗但係暗地裡同太一係hehe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先逐個進成熟期但係巴達獸遲遲進唔到，原來係玩救世主設定打第一個boss惡魔獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後打悟空獸，太一嘅迷失令到麥樂雞獸錯誤進化成喪屍暴龍獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後成功修正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到打吸血魔獸然後去返現實世界，兩隻天使加兩隻究極體嘅預言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後四大天王逐個打，鋼鐵海龍同機械邪龍都被戰鬥暴龍剋死，再到小丑王完全唔夠打，天使威能又出場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個節奏都好正，可惜之後得04可以拍得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後作仲要寫柒天使獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6014949f6fe267fbd28fe9b8447669ad1995e237","tid":858222,"uid":833,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:01:06.000Z","msg":"竟然冇提打到返現實世界東京台場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲冇提最尾拋帽清唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2e814ecbcc1179ec113db82994728e8474e44e","tid":858222,"uid":14486,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:04:13.000Z","msg":"巨鯨獸，獅子獸同妖精獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ceee1baf554bda13533153a198e8fe8bf3c1d8","tid":858222,"uid":16384,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T23:31:53.000Z","msg":"03&gt;01"},{"pid":"db077bc732c986bb2dd86b09f3b9910be90bbcdd","tid":858222,"uid":141869,"like":11,"dislike"